---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Sambulo Senda — Mobile Engineer" description="Mobile engineer, indie app maker, and consultant helping teams ship React Native apps.">
  <main class="min-h-screen flex flex-col">

    <section class="pt-16 pb-20 sm:pt-24 flex-1">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">

        <h1 class="reveal text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-ink tracking-tight mb-8 font-sans" style="--i: 0">
          Sambulo Senda
        </h1>

        <div class="reveal space-y-5 text-ink-muted text-lg leading-relaxed" style="--i: 1">
          <p>
            I'm a mobile engineer. I build React Native apps, some my own, others for clients who need their apps to actually ship.
          </p>
          <p>
            Most of my time goes to the hard parts: making apps fast on slow devices, getting offline sync right, and solving the problems that don't have a Stack Overflow answer. I <a href="/writing" class="text-ink underline underline-offset-4 decoration-ink-faint hover:decoration-ink transition-colors">write</a> about what I learn along the way.
          </p>
          <p>
            Some of my favorite writing:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li><a href="/blog/react-native-0-78-react-19-updates" class="text-ink underline underline-offset-4 decoration-ink-faint hover:decoration-ink transition-colors">React Native 0.78 & React 19</a></li>
            <li><a href="/blog/building-offline-first-react-native" class="text-ink underline underline-offset-4 decoration-ink-faint hover:decoration-ink transition-colors">Building Offline-First React Native</a></li>
            <li><a href="/blog/react-native-perfomance-tips" class="text-ink underline underline-offset-4 decoration-ink-faint hover:decoration-ink transition-colors">React Native Performance Tips</a></li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            You can <a href="/writing" class="text-ink underline underline-offset-4 decoration-ink-faint hover:decoration-ink transition-colors">read my writing</a> or <a href="https://cal.com/sambulosenda" class="text-ink underline underline-offset-4 decoration-ink-faint hover:decoration-ink transition-colors">reach out</a> if interested.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <Footer />

  </main>
</Layout>
